name: Supahands Dotcom Sdn Bhd
description: Developer of a data labeling platform designed to accurately label images, text, speech, and video clips. The company's platform uses artificial intelligence technology and offers Application Programming Interface (API) integration in real-time and proprietary data labeling tools, enabling businesses to deliver an accurate training dataset that is ready for use.
